summary: This Subscription Agreement is between Greenpro Capital Corp., a Nevada corporation, and a Purchaser, outlining the sale of common stock shares at $1.30 per share under exemptions from registration. The agreement specifies the terms of the sale, representations and warranties from both parties, and the closing details, including the location and method of payment.
